curam.util.ieg.impl
Class QuestionPageResult

java.lang.Object
  curam.util.ieg.impl.QuestionPageResult

public class QuestionPageResult
extends java.lang.Object

The QuestionPageResult class represents a summary of question pages that have been presented to the user. The result pages do not include any of the textual elements of the question pages.
